game.name: First Day Of School Preps
game.description:
Rachel and her cute little sister are ready to go to college and school respectively. Annie studies in the second grade while Rachel is in the college. After a long vacation, they both enjoyed some good time together at their home, but now it is time to join the studies again. These two beautiful sisters need your help to prepare the awesome outfits for the first day of college and school. Why do not you join them to guide to pick up the perfect school outfits in First Day of School Preps?

Start with Rachel by dressing her up with a green plaid outfit over a white color short sleeved shirt along with a red color tie! You can also opt for a purple and white stripped knitted crop top and combine it an orange skirt or a pink color outfit with polka dots and pair it with a denim jacket. She would also fabulous with a black denim skirt, a black top, white cardigan and pink scarf along with a pair of cool jeans. An orange and green varsity jacket with a mustard sweater will look nice on her. 
Complete her look with a butterfly in her hair and a purple backpack with some ethnic prints in this one of the best HTML5 dressing games for girls! Now prepare the school outfit for her little sister. She loves carrying an orange vest over a blue plaid shirt along with a ruffled skirt. Challenge your fashion sense to prepare the jaw-dropping looks for these two beauties in this new girls game! Try out more dress-up school games and have a blast killing your time without download
